# NeuroSync — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your keys.

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  PRIMARY AI PROVIDER — Groq (REQUIRED for app to function)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Groq powers all text-only AI features in NeuroSync:
#   • Helpful Chat (streaming)
#   • Behavior Interpreter (text mode)
#   • Diet & Nutrition Planner (generating meal plans)
#   • Therapy Scheduler (scheduling support)
#   • Homeschool Lesson Generator (learning plans)
#   • Visual Board (emoji-to-sentence descriptions)
#   • Emergency Support (de-escalation guidance)
#   • Child Progress Reports (narrative generation)
#   • Cue Interpreter (audio event interpretation)
#
# Setup:
#   1. Go to https://console.groq.com
#   2. Sign up (free, no credit card needed)
#   3. Create an API key under "API Keys"
#   4. Paste below
#
# Quota: 14,400 requests/day on free tier — sufficient for active development
#
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here
# GROQ_MODEL=llama-3.3-70b-versatile   # default: best text quality

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  HANDWRITING INTERPRETER — Mistral (REQUIRED for handwriting analysis only)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Mistral is used for handwriting vision interpretation in the local service.
# The app sends handwriting images to Mistral and returns structured transcription
# and pattern analysis for dyslexia-aware handwriting feedback.
#
# Setup:
#   1. Go to https://www.mistral.ai/
#   2. Create an API key
#   3. Paste below
#
# Quota: depends on your Mistral plan; use a real key for handwriting analysis.
#
MISTRAL_API_KEY=your_mistral_api_key_here
# MISTRAL_MODEL=mistral-small-latest

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  HANDWRITING SERVICE — Python Microservice (local, recommended)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Microservice that connects to Gemini for vision-based handwriting analysis.
# Can run locally or be deployed separately.
#
# Setup (one-time):
#   cd handwriting-service
#   python -m venv .venv
#   .venv\Scripts\activate        # Windows
#   source .venv/bin/activate     # Mac/Linux
#   pip install -r requirements.txt
#
# Start:
#   .venv\Scripts\uvicorn.exe app.main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8001   # Windows
#   source .venv/bin/activate && uvicorn app.main:app --port 8001        # Mac/Linux
#
# Or as part of dev setup:
#   npm run dev:full-with-handwriting  # (if script exists)
#
HANDWRITING_SERVICE_URL=http://localhost:8001

# SQLite path (default: ./neurosync.db)
# DB_PATH=/data/neurosync.db

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  AUDIO FILE STORAGE
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Where uploaded audio recordings are saved on disk.
# Clips are auto-deleted after 30 days (DPDP §8 retention).
# Default: ./uploads
#
# UPLOADS_DIR=/data/uploads

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  ML SIDECAR — Python FastAPI (local, strongly recommended)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Provides real MFCC audio embeddings via librosa + ffmpeg.
# Falls back to a JS approximation if unreachable.
#
# Setup (one-time, Python 3.10+):
#   cd ml
#   python -m venv .venv
#   .venv\Scripts\activate        # Windows
#   source .venv/bin/activate     # Mac/Linux
#   pip install -r requirements.txt
#
# Start alongside Node:
#   npm run dev:full              # starts both Node + sidecar together
#
# Requires ffmpeg installed system-wide (winget install Gyan.FFmpeg on Windows)
#
ML_SIDECAR_URL=http://localhost:8000

# Path to ffmpeg binary — only needed if ffmpeg is not on PATH
# FFMPEG_PATH=C:\Users\YourName\AppData\Local\Microsoft\WinGet\Links\ffmpeg.exe

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  MULTILINGUAL — Bhashini (India GOI, optional)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Leave unset for English-only mode (safe default).
# Register at: https://bhashini.gov.in/ulca
#
# BHASHINI_API_KEY=your_bhashini_key
# BHASHINI_ENDPOINT=https://dhruva-api.bhashini.gov.in/services/inference/pipeline

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  EMAIL — SMTP (optional, for sending reports and admin CSV exports)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Provide credentials for an SMTP relay, mailgun/sendgrid SMTP interface, or other mail service.
#
SMTP_HOST=smtp.example.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_SECURE=false
SMTP_USER=your_smtp_username
SMTP_PASS=your_smtp_password
# SMTP_FROM="NeuroSync <no-reply@example.com>"

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  YOUTUBE DATA API v3 (optional, for lesson video thumbnails)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Used by the Lesson Planner to show relevant YouTube video thumbnails per step.
# Key is stored server-side ONLY — never sent to the browser.
#
# Setup:
#   1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com
#   2. Create a project → Enable "YouTube Data API v3"
#   3. Create an API key (restrict to YouTube Data API v3)
#   Free tier: 10,000 units/day — each search costs 100 units.
#   Results are cached for 24h per topic+difficulty, so real usage is minimal.
#
# YOUTUBE_API_KEY=AIza...

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  SERVER
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# PORT=3000
# NODE_ENV=production
